Code : Star Pattern
Send Feedback
Print the following pattern
Pattern for N = 4
     *
    * *
   * * *
  * * * *
The dots represent spaces.

Input Format :
N (Total no. of rows)
Output Format :
Pattern in N lines





#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
int n;
cin>>n;
for(int i=1; i<=n; i++){
	for(int spaces=1; spaces<=n-i; spaces++){
		cout<<" ";
	}
	for(int j=1; j<=2*i-1; j++){
		cout<<"*";
	}
	cout<<endl;
}
}



